# Optional override for calling a backend on a different host.
# For local development, you usually do NOT need this because the frontend defaults to
# calling `/api` and CRA's `proxy` (in package.json) forwards to http://localhost:5000.
#
# Example:
# REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# Production examples (set these in Vercel Project Environment Variables):
# REACT_APP_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.com/api
# REACT_APP_QUESTION_API_URL=https://your-question-api-domain.com
# REACT_APP_MCQ_EXTRACT_API_URL=https://your-mcq-api-domain.com
